@Barry Ancona
When my eyes scanned across your name just now, I read it as "anaconda." I suspect 35A had something to do with that. 
Cheers

@Francis

Oh, come on now. I mean, sure — *most* people around here do seem to cheat pretty regularly (but using “lookups” to preserve their streaks, rather than cheating honestly), but surely not the crowd Jake G was addressing.

Speaking for myself, as someone who usually finishes well below the xwstats median times (while solving on an iPad), but nowhere near the crazy-fast tournament times: do lots of Fridays and Saturdays in the archives! That, or spend 40+ years solving like Steve said.

@Jake G

