@Jake G
Crosswords are no different than loading a furniture truck. Some people are better at it than others. I’m an expert. Crosswords are a hobby/pastime for me (50+ years now)
I’m a hunt and peck typist so it takes me longer. 40 minutes today. While I no longer pack furniture trucks, I can still do crossword puzzles. Happily so!

@Deb
I /loved/ 39A! I got it immediately-- no idea how, I'm no herpetologist. I don't remember a surfeit of snaky solves lately either. Sssssometimes you're jusssst given a gift.
🐍

@Chris

I started with MutantS crossing unadornEd for 1d/14a.

Still came together within a second of my Sat. average.

@Matt

