Guess I dodged a bullet there, because it sounds like my concept of h-e-double-toothpicks.

@Matt
Oy, that would have killed me. I worked at a camp in the 70s for a few summers, but luckily it was more of a New Games vibe. btw searching "new games" leads to a ton of hits about video games. I had to add terms to get to the 1976 book.

